DESCRIPTION:Report writing focus:\n• Relaxed timetable to plan time to c
 omplete pupil mentoring\, page 1\n• Plan a lesson to discuss and write:\
 n  • What have you learnt/improved on this year?\n  • What did you enj
 oy about this year?\n  • Next year\, what will you aim to improve on?\n 
