 o write this neatly on lined paper\n• Office – make labels “To the P
 arent/Carer of xxxxx” and put on envelopes\n• Following all assessment
 s completed\, update RAG rating for reading\, writing and maths for the su
 mmer term on page 1 of the report\n• Add attendance percentage to front 
